Definition: usually short) marked by some action or condition
Example: he was here for a little while; I need to rest for a piece; a spell of good weather; a patch of bad weather
Synonyms: piece, spell, patch, time, a, period, of, indeterminate, length, usually, short, marked, by, some, action, or, condition, he, was, here, for, little, I, need, to, rest, good, weather, bad
Category: noun.time
